"{\"uid\": \"thenorthlines.com-japanese-wrestler-empathizes-with-vinesh-phogat-after-near-miss-at-olympics-qualification\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Athletes often find themselves narrowly missing out on achievements and opportunities due to small margins.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two wrestlers recently experienced this and can relate to each other's frustrations.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rei Higuchi of Japan, who won the 57kg freestyle gold at the Paris Olympics, reached out in support of India's Vinesh Phogat.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 193, \"end\": 204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rei Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}, {\"begin\": 208, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.8680448146304227, \"rank\": 0.1499828400082015, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8620358598049518, \"rank\": 0.08524941116975901, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Higuchi himself knows the pain of a close call all too well.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Asia qualifiers for the Tokyo Games, he missed making weight by a slight 50 grams and was disqualified.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he was able to make a strong comeback winning gold at the recent Olympics in France.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5386085225779258, \"rank\": 0.7538673947110213, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his success, Higuchi has not forgotten the disappointment of the past.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh suffered a similar heartbreak in her quest to compete at the previous Olympics.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She fell short of her target weight by 100 grams at the qualifiers and had to sit out of the Tokyo event.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999099556263734, \"rank\": 5.9997807892910734e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reaction back home was fierce with many feeling the decision lacked fairness.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even abroad, fellow wrestlers like Jordan Burroughs and Sarah Hildebrandt voiced their support for the Indian.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Burroughs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Burroughs\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999920419, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}, {\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9860178790091426, \"rank\": 0.013954931237960889, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now following his Paris victory, Higuchi reached out to Vinesh on social media.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999816225229, \"rank\": 1.83774744342301e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He urged her not to listen to outside voices and emphasized that overcoming difficulties is what truly matters.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Japanese wrestler said he understands her feelings completely since they both narrowly failed to qualify by small margins earlier.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9676020279809681, \"rank\": 0.03034926713422313, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He advised Vinesh to take rest after facing criticism and believes rising above setbacks marks real strength of character.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is commendable to see Olympic champions lifting up others who have struggled in their shadow.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Higuchi proving his sportsmanship by sharing Vinesh's pain and encouraging her future demonstrates the bonds between athletes worldwide.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rei_Higuchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Higuchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q1908